  "verticals": {
    "description": "Multi-tenant verticals managed via src/verticals/<id>/. Each vertical is a catalog + starter kits consumed by tenants in sites/<slug>/. Unlike `types` above (flat beauty-era pattern), verticals support i18n, hreflang, per-tenant content, site-scoped leads, and sublinear scaling to new countries/tenants.",
